# Prompt: Implement Complete SEO Tools Suite for phung.work
## Objective
Build a professional **SEO Tools** module for **phung.work**, providing a collection of browser-first SEO utilities for developers, marketers, bloggers, and website owners.
The goal is to create SEO tools comparable to TechnicalSEO, Ahrefs Free Tools, SEMRush Tools, Moz, SmallSEOTools, and SEO Review Tools.
All tools should follow the existing architecture, design system, reusable components, and routing conventions already used by phung.work.
---
# Core Principles
* Privacy-first.
* Run completely in the browser whenever possible.
* No backend for local processing tools.
* API integration should be optional and isolated.
* Fast and responsive.
* Mobile friendly.
* Dark mode support.
* Accessible (WCAG AA).
* Modular architecture.
* Reusable components.
* TypeScript-first.
* Lazy loading and code splitting.
Do not change the existing application architecture unless absolutely necessary.
